{"type":null,"faqId":33137,"title":"GPS地理闹钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>每款智能手机都有内置闹钟功能，这次，地理闹钟，与传统时间闹钟，有点不同。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以从“备忘录-&gt;新建-&gt;地理闹钟”揭开她的面纱，分为智能出行、指定位置、指定时间，三种闹钟类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>智能出行提醒，会根据你设置的时间和目的地，结合当时的时间、位置、路况等条件，向你发送智能提醒，并能安排合理的行进路线，地理闹钟会告诉你最佳的出行时间；位置提醒，当经过设置的目的地时，闹钟会提醒你完成要做的事情，紧张忙碌的生活得到合理的规划。</span><span class=\"s1\">比</span><span>如你在地理闹钟里设定了去超市打酱油，当你经过超市附近时，地理闹钟就会主动提醒你。位置提醒需要在GPS卫星信号良好的情况下使用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果你常常忘记规划自己的工作、学习和生活，那么手机的地理闹钟就是你最贴心的伙伴。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7839","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748511000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":38,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"备忘录,地理闹钟","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}